OL,3,CWoman tells of six-year wait to
OL,4,Creceive Premium Bonds after father's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FA woman from Newbury has described how
OL,8,Fit took nearly six years to receive
OL,9,F#2,000 in Premium Bonds from NS&I
OL,10,Fafter her father died.
OL,12,FTracy McGuire-Brown said she had a
OL,13,F"very long and drawn-out" experience
OL,14,Fdealing with NS&I, eventually
OL,15,Freceiving what she was entitled to
OL,16,Flast month.
OL,18,FShe said her father died in 2020 and
OL,19,F"after he died, obviously there were a
OL,20,Flot of affairs to sort out and we knew
OL,21,Fhe had some Premium Bonds".
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@YO]{D@AOU}D@ZO]
