PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1774624292
OL,3,CWoman tells of six-year wait to
OL,4,Creceive Premium Bonds after father's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FThe 61-year-old said NS&I was
OL,8,Fcontacted several times but initially
OL,9,Fsaid there was no such account, "even
OL,10,Fthough we gave all the details and
OL,11,Fmore and explained the situation".
OL,13,F"Finally in 2024, we started to get
OL,14,Fsome movement that there was an
OL,15,Faccount and eventually they said yes
OL,16,Fthere was and then it started."
OL,18,FShe said she sent various documents by
OL,19,Fpost, adding "there would be weeks in
OL,20,Fbetween" and "still it went on".
OL,26,@qD@aOUsD@aO]uD@AOUxD@_O]{D@NOU|D@HO]|D@
OL,26,ANOU|D@_O]
