OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1774624292
OL,3,CWoman tells of six-year wait to
OL,4,Creceive Premium Bonds after father's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FThe former care home manager said she
OL,8,Feventually received a letter
OL,9,Fsuggesting that before the money was
OL,10,Fused she should pay off any debts or
OL,11,Ffuneral expenses. She added: "My
OL,12,Ffather had been dead five years by
OL,13,Fthen, I just found that was the final
OL,14,Finsult."
OL,26,@sD@^OUvD@HO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
