FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1774624292
OL,3,CWoman tells of six-year wait to
OL,4,Creceive Premium Bonds after father's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FAfter complaining, she received #150
OL,8,F"to say sorry for all the expenses
OL,9,Fthat I'd had, but that doesn't cover
OL,10,Fthe distress, the time, you know, and
OL,11,Fit was #2,000, we weren't talking
OL,12,Fhundreds of thousands... it was just
OL,13,Fridiculous, it was a horrible time".
OL,15,FShe added: "Really, should it be that
OL,16,Fdifficult, that awful and that much of
OL,17,Fa trial?
OL,19,F"It's just frightening, really. To
OL,20,Fmake it so difficult and so
OL,21,Finsensitive is just appalling, I think.
OL,26,@pD@AOUuD@cO]wD@LOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
