PN,41905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1774624292
OL,3,CWoman tells of six-year wait to
OL,4,Creceive Premium Bonds after father's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,F"The weeks that passed by in between
OL,8,Fand the hoops that you had to jump
OL,9,Fthrough.
OL,11,F"Even when you have got all the
OL,12,Finformation and you give them all the
OL,13,Finformation, my experience was
OL,14,Fappalling... to the extent that I
OL,15,Fdefinitely would not invest in Premium
OL,16,FBonds now.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
