OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1774624292
OL,3,CWoman tells of six-year wait to
OL,4,Creceive Premium Bonds after father's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,F"And that's a shame... when you are
OL,8,Fdealing with the bereavement of a
OL,9,Fclose relative, to have this just keep
OL,10,Fgoing on, it just rakes stuff up as
OL,11,Fwell, you just want to sort it, that's
OL,12,Fall."
OL,14,FShe highlighted continuity issues in
OL,15,Fthe process when she was speaking to
OL,16,FNS&I staff, "so if you did get to
OL,17,Fspeak to someone you had to explain
OL,18,Feverything again and again and again,
OL,19,Fjust really bad".
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@EO]xD@MOU{D@PO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
