PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1774624292
OL,3,CWoman tells of six-year wait to
OL,4,Creceive Premium Bonds after father's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FOn Thursday, it emerged that NS&I,
OL,8,Fwhich is backed by the Treasury, is
OL,9,Fpreparing to pay out hundreds of
OL,10,Fmillions of pounds after failures
OL,11,Fmeant that bereaved families were
OL,12,Fmissing out on savings pots.
OL,14,FPensions minister Torsten Bell said
OL,15,FNS&I has reviewed more than 34 million
OL,16,Fcustomer records.
OL,18,FHe said: "That work is ongoing, but it
OL,19,Fpoints to a maximum of around 37,500
OL,20,Fcustomers with up to #476 million in
OL,21,Fdeposits being affected.
OL,26,@zD@JOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
