OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1774624292
OL,3,CWoman tells of six-year wait to
OL,4,Creceive Premium Bonds after father's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,F"Three-quarters of cases relate to the
OL,8,Fperiod between 2008 and 2025."
OL,10,FHe said this number is likely to fall
OL,11,F"but while it represents less than
OL,12,F0.2% of NS&I's customers, it is still
OL,13,Ffar too many".
OL,15,FIn a statement an NS&I spokesperson
OL,16,Fsaid: "We recognise that dealing with
OL,17,Fbereavement can be challenging and
OL,18,Fwould like to apologise to anyone who
OL,19,Fhas not received the customer service
OL,20,Ffrom NS&I that they should expect,
OL,21,Fparticularly at such a sensitive time."
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@^O]sD@AOUuD@MO]xD@GOU}D@gO]
